1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 24=

3
00:00:56,479 --> 00:00:57,119
Don't cry.

4
00:00:59,280 --> 00:00:59,880
Ji Xuan.

5
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:08,159
I thought I'd never see you again.

6
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:09,280
That won't happen.

7
00:01:11,519 --> 00:01:13,439
- Prepare for the surgery.
- Yes, Mr. Song.

8
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:19,359
(To find a kidney donor,)

9
00:01:19,719 --> 00:01:21,000
(he also underwent tests,)

10
00:01:21,519 --> 00:01:22,959
(preparing to give his kidney)

11
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,480
(to your mom.)

12
00:01:26,879 --> 00:01:28,799
Are you going to donate your own kidney?

13
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:29,680
What?

14
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:31,079
No, Song.

15
00:01:31,319 --> 00:01:33,599
I'd rather die than take your kidney.

16
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,400
Madam, listen to me.

17
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:36,959
There's nothing more to say.

18
00:01:37,159 --> 00:01:38,519
I'm not treating my illness.

19
00:01:38,519 --> 00:01:39,519
Stay calm, Mom.

20
00:01:39,519 --> 00:01:40,760
- Send me home.
- Mr. Song.

21
00:01:41,959 --> 00:01:42,480
Mr. Song.

22
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,719
The kidney donor is found.

23
00:02:22,299 --> 00:02:28,832
(Three Months Later)

24
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:40,280
Ji Xuan.

25
00:02:46,639 --> 00:02:47,280
Come here.

26
00:03:04,479 --> 00:03:05,319
So beautiful.

27
00:03:16,479 --> 00:03:17,719
Seems not much has changed.

28
00:03:17,919 --> 00:03:20,840
Over there is the library,
the teaching building, and a playground.

29
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:22,400
Missing old days?

30
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:25,000
A little bit.

31
00:03:25,439 --> 00:03:26,439
Me too.

32
00:03:28,432 --> 00:03:32,653
ظآزMissing you, missing youظآز

33
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:35,904
ظآزYou come to my dreamظآز

34
00:03:35,904 --> 00:03:40,595
ظآزMissing you, missing youظآز

35
00:03:43,296 --> 00:03:48,861
ظآزCan you still hear meظآز

36
00:03:50,944 --> 00:03:54,976
ظآزCan I wash for your loveظآز

37
00:03:58,491 --> 00:03:59,712
(Ji Xuan, First Prize of the 7th
National Youth Design Competition)

38
00:03:59,712 --> 00:04:01,472
ظآزLoving you, loving youظآز

39
00:04:01,879 --> 00:04:03,400
Thank you.

40
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,159
Truly amazing.

41
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,159
Exactly.

42
00:04:06,976 --> 00:04:11,099
ظآزLoving you, loving youظآز

43
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,599
It's been half a year already.

44
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:18,000
Don't you owe me an explanation?

45
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,000
What explanation?

46
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:25,040
I've worked tirelessly
for your new company.

47
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,639
Shouldn't you give me a proper title?

48
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,120
I'll think about it.

49
00:04:32,519 --> 00:04:33,360
Are you serious?

50
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:36,759
Didn't I work hard enough last night?

51
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,439
Song Zhaoli, this is a school.

52
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,040
Wait for me.

53
00:05:00,014 --> 00:05:01,696
(Big Wontons)

54
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:07,399
When I was in school,
I often came to this restaurant.

55
00:05:07,399 --> 00:05:10,040
Xiao Jin was that stingy?
He usually only brought you here?

56
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:12,560
Thank you.

57
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,120
Thank you.

58
00:05:14,759 --> 00:05:17,319
I remember you. You used to come often.

59
00:05:17,399 --> 00:05:18,920
You graduated five or six years ago.

60
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,240
Good memory.

61
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,720
Boyfriend?

62
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:25,480
I brought him to see where I studied.

63
00:05:27,399 --> 00:05:28,800
I think I've seen you before.

64
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,519
Have you been to my shop?

65
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:32,519
You came every Friday.

66
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:34,680
Sometimes, you even left a tip.

67
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:35,839
You made a mistake.

68
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,959
I'm from Qingcheng.

69
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,600
How could I have come here?

70
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:39,639
Is that so?

71
00:05:42,839 --> 00:05:43,439
Try it.

72
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,639
Sour.

73
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,319
Impossible.

74
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,279
It's not sour.

75
00:05:59,079 --> 00:06:00,040
I'm jealous.

76
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,000
You had a first love.

77
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:06,199
She must have mistaken me for Xiao Jin.

78
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:11,160
Enough, Song Zhaoli.

79
00:06:11,639 --> 00:06:13,879
I don't believe
you never had a first love.

80
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,480
To be honest,

81
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,439
I did have one.

82
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:53,439
Hello, are you from our school?

83
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:54,519
No.

84
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:55,019
Why?

85
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:57,560
Then do you have a girlfriend?

86
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:02,920
That was my ex-girlfriend.
I haven't forgotten her yet.

87
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:19,319
Song Zhaoli, stop pretending.

88
00:07:19,839 --> 00:07:20,639
What?

89
00:07:25,573 --> 00:07:28,672
(Enter Password)

90
00:07:30,879 --> 00:07:32,480
How did you know my phone password?

91
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,519
My birthday. Is it hard to guess?

92
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,040
I was careless.

93
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,240
Alright.

94
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,104
I'll confess.

95
00:07:39,959 --> 00:07:41,600
I took Mr. Qiu's account

96
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:43,959
and then impersonated him
to message you.

97
00:07:46,319 --> 00:07:46,819
That's all?

98
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:48,399
Sure.

99
00:07:57,199 --> 00:07:58,959
Don't tell me these photos

100
00:07:58,959 --> 00:08:00,439
were all sent to you by Liao Bei?

101
00:08:01,199 --> 00:08:02,879
Fine, I admit it.

102
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:06,680
Actually, the shop owner
wasn't mistaken.

103
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:10,600
Every Friday night,
I would go to your school to see you.

104
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:13,560
Ji Xuan, I really like you.

105
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:17,279
I like you very much.

106
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,720
If I didn't find out,

107
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,759
how long would you keep it from me?

108
00:08:26,399 --> 00:08:27,120
For a lifetime.

109
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,079
Is it worth it?

110
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,480
Ji Xuan.

111
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:33,360
You are my only love.

112
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,240
So for you,

113
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:38,200
everything I do is worth it.

114
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:07,600
Go ahead.

115
00:09:08,279 --> 00:09:09,039
You go.

116
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,440
Let's go together.

117
00:09:28,679 --> 00:09:30,399
Okay, time to launch.

118
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:33,759
Launch.

119
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:34,639
Huan.

120
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,080
