121
00:09:36,799 --> 00:09:39,519
We want to talk with you.

122
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:40,639
Okay.

123
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:41,240
Huan.

124
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:44,120
How did you end up last
in the class on the final exam?

125
00:09:44,159 --> 00:09:46,320
Are you having any problems
with your studies?

126
00:09:48,799 --> 00:09:50,120
I want to repeat a year.

127
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:50,840
Why?

128
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:54,159
If I repeat a year,
I can be in the same class

129
00:09:54,159 --> 00:09:56,639
