130
00:09:59,879 --> 00:10:01,000
Mom, what's wrong?

131
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:01,639
What's wrong?

132
00:10:03,919 --> 00:10:05,080
Song Yile is coming.

133
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,559
My baby sister is coming.

134
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:09,559
My baby sister is coming.

